001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.selenium;
002
003import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.ComponentType;
004import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.tab.TabService;
005
006/**
007 * Represents a UI element for tab components within the framework.
008 *
009 * <p>This interface extends {@link UiElement} and provides a default implementation
010 * for retrieving the associated component type, ensuring that tab elements
011 * can be interacted with in a standardized manner.
012 *
013 * <p>Tabs allow users to switch between different sections of content in a UI.
014 * This interface facilitates automation of tab interactions, such as selecting,
015 * validating visibility, and checking if a tab is enabled or selected.
016 *
017 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
018 */
019public interface TabUiElement extends UiElement {
020
021   /**
022    * Retrieves the component type associated with this tab element.
023    *
024    * <p>The default implementation returns {@link TabService#DEFAULT_TYPE},
025    * ensuring that the tab element is recognized as part of the tab service.
026    *
027    * @param <T> The component type.
028    * @return The component type associated with this tab element.
029    */
030   @Override
031   default <T extends ComponentType> T componentType() {
032      return (T) TabService.DEFAULT_TYPE;
033   }
034
035}
